<BaseLayout title="What is Feng Shui · The Beginner's Guide · cusprose" path="/guides/what-is-feng-shui/" description="Feng shui is the Chinese art of arranging space so energy moves well through it. Here's what it is — the bagua, the five elements, qi — demystified, not superstitious.">
