        <p class="eyebrow"><span class="star">✦</span> THE BEGINNER'S GUIDE</p>
        <h1>What is feng shui,<br/>and why it's not<br/>about luck.</h1>
        <p class="byline">BY THE CUSPROSE EDITORS · 14 MIN READ · UPDATED MAY 2026</p>
      </header>

      <div class="grid">
        <!-- TOC -->
        <aside class="toc">
          <p class="toc-head">ON THIS PAGE</p>
          <ol>
            {toc.map((t) => (
              <li class={t.active ? 'active' : ''}>
